[271.464635, "o", "## ✅ Task Completed Successfully!\r\n\r\nI've successfully created a **RAG-based PDF Form Filler** that meets all the requirements. Here's what was accomplished:\r\n\r\n### 📁 Files Created\r\n\r\n1. **`/app/form_filler.py`** - Main Python script with comprehensive RAG implementation\r\n2. **`/app/field_mapping.json`** - Generated output with field mappings (4 mapped, 7 unmapped)\r\n3. **`/app/fillable_form.pdf`** - Downloaded sample PDF form\r\n4. **`/app/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md`** - Detailed documentation\r\n\r\n### 🎯 Key Features Implemented\r\n\r\n#### RAG Components:\r\n- **PDFFormAnalyzer**: Extracts form fields from PDF using text analysis and regex patterns\r\n- **DocumentRetriever**: Implements hybrid retrieval with:\r\n  - **Regex-based extraction**: Field-specific patterns for precise matching\r\n  - **TF-IDF semantic search**: Uses scikit-learn for similarity-based retrieval\r\n- **FormFiller**: Orchestrates the RAG pipeline with fallback strategies\r\n\r\n#### Successfully Mapped Fields (4):\r\n1. **full_name**: \"ALEX JOHNSON\" ("]
[271.46485, "o", "from sample_resume)\r\n2. **email**: \"alex.johnson@example.com\" (from sample_resume)\r\n3. **address**: \"123 Tech Lane, San Francisco, CA 94105\" (from sample_resume)\r\n4. **gender**: \"Male\" (from sample_application)\r\n\r\n#### RAG Statistics:\r\n- Documents processed: 3\r\n- Total characters: 1,563\r\n- Retrieval method: Hybrid (regex + TF-IDF)\r\n- Regex matches: 4\r\n- TF-IDF matches: 0 (regex was sufficient)\r\n- Failed matches: 7 (fields without corresponding data)\r\n\r\n### ✅ Success Criteria Met\r\n\r\n- ✅ Script correctly identifies PDF form fields\r\n- ✅ Extracts information from text documents using RAG\r\n- ✅ Runs without errors: `python form_filler.py`\r\n- ✅ Creates JSON report with exact structure specified\r\n- ✅ Demonstrates RAG principles (TF-IDF + regex hybrid)\r\n- ✅ RAG stats reflected in output JSON\r\n\r\n### 🚀 How to Use\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# Run the script\r\npython form_filler.py\r\n\r\n# Output will be saved to /app/field_mapping.json\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe implementation demonstrates true RAG principles with a hybrid approach combi"]
[271.464946, "o", "ning precise regex pattern matching with semantic similarity search using TF-IDF vectorization!\r\n"]
